(secondQuint)Effects of Pectin Supplementation in Diarrhea-predominant Irritable Bowel Syndrome.

 Patients were randomized to receive either pectin or placebo.

 Treatment consisted of 6 weeks supplementation with pectin (fiber group) or placebo (maltodextrin).

 We evaluated the clinical symptoms, gut microbiota and the immune markers in two groups.

